
# Customer Churn Prediction System

# Overview
End-to-end machine learning solution predicting customer churn with **80.2% accuracy** using XGBoost.

##  Tech Stack
- **Python**: Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, XGBoost
- **Web**: Flask, HTML, CSS
- **Tools**: Jupyter, VS Code, Git

## Model Performance
| Metric | Score |
|--------|-------|
| Accuracy | 80.2% |
| Precision (Churn) | 64% |

##  How to Run
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
